						<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-green-800">When do you take down the lights?</h3>
						<p class="text-gray-700">Takedown is included in all our packages. We typically schedule takedown in early January, but can accommodate different timing based on your preferences.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-md">
